WEBVTT

00:08.942 --> 00:12.412
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE

00:12.479 --> 00:16.783
A DIVISION OF TIME WARNER
ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY, L.P.

00:39.172 --> 00:42.041
WOULD YOU KNOW
THE DEVIL IF YOU SAW HIM ?

00:42.108 --> 00:44.477
WOULD YOU KNOW
HIS FACE, HIS EYES ?

00:44.544 --> 00:46.679
WOULD YOU FEEL CHILLED
IN HIS PRESENCE ?

00:46.746 --> 00:48.848
OR DO YOU THINK
HE'S SOME NAKED RED GUY

00:48.915 --> 00:51.518
WITH HORNS AND A GOATEE
AND A TAIL ?

00:51.584 --> 00:53.853
I'M TODD McFARLANE,
CREATOR OF "SPAWN".

00:53.920 --> 00:57.023
TRUE EVIL IS NEVER
WHAT OR WHO YOU EXPECT.

00:57.090 --> 00:59.993
SOMETIMES IT'S GROTESQUE,
SOMETIMES IT'S BEAUTIFUL,

01:00.059 --> 01:02.762
SOMETIMES IT'S A MOBSTER
OR A PRIEST,

01:02.829 --> 01:04.864
EVEN THE
ICE CREAM MAN.

01:04.931 --> 01:07.734
FOR ALL YOU KNOW,
I COULD BE TRUE EVIL.

01:07.801 --> 01:09.569
SCARY, HUH ?

01:09.636 --> 01:13.406
MOST OF ALL, TRUE EVIL
WHISPERS WHAT WE WANNA HEAR,

01:13.473 --> 01:15.408
AND WHEN IT
SHOWS ITS UGLY FACE,

01:15.475 --> 01:17.477
IT TELLS US
TO DO NOTHING.

01:17.544 --> 01:19.546
AND THAT'S WHERE
WE FIND SPAWN,

01:19.612 --> 01:23.082
SITTING IN THE SHADOWS
DOING ABSOLUTELY NOTHING.

01:31.124 --> 01:32.459
WHAT YOU GOT
THERE IS BIG.

01:32.525 --> 01:34.694
A LATENT PRINT OFF
THE GIRL'S EYEBALL.

01:34.761 --> 01:36.930
KYLE WATSON WAS SET UP
TO TAKE THE FALL

01:36.996 --> 01:38.164
FOR THOSE
CHILD MURDERS.

01:38.231 --> 01:40.533
THIS SON-OF-A-BITCH
WAS PURPOSELY MISFILED,

01:40.600 --> 01:42.635
VAULTED AND BURIED.

01:44.237 --> 01:46.706
WHY ARE YOU
FOLLOWING HER ?!

01:46.773 --> 01:48.708
I WANT ANSWERS, NOW !

01:49.943 --> 01:51.978
A GUY FALLS
OUT OF A TREE,

01:52.045 --> 01:52.946
THEN BLOWS
HIS BRAINS OUT,

01:53.012 --> 01:53.947
FOR WHAT ?

01:54.013 --> 01:56.449
THIS PHOTOGRAPHER'S
FROM WASHINGTON D.C.

01:56.516 --> 01:58.518
FOR THE U.S.
GOVERNMENT.

01:58.585 --> 02:00.753
WE LOST A LARGE
NUMBER OF WEAPONS

02:00.820 --> 02:03.022
FROM THAT ORDNANCE
ANNEX A WEEK AGO.

02:03.089 --> 02:03.923
WHO COULD'VE
DONE THIS ?

02:03.990 --> 02:06.493
IT MAY HAVE BEEN
AN INSIDE JOB SIR.

02:06.559 --> 02:07.994
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT ?

02:08.061 --> 02:09.162
IT'S HERE
IN MY REPORT.

02:09.229 --> 02:10.797
GODAMN BOY SCOUT !

02:10.864 --> 02:12.699
THE LAST THING I NEED
IS HIM TURNING HEADS

02:12.765 --> 02:14.000
BY TALKING
TO SOMEONE.

02:14.067 --> 02:15.668
WE GOT SOME HEAVY
DUTY SHIT HERE.

02:15.735 --> 02:17.270
AND I NEED THAT DISK.

02:17.337 --> 02:20.039
I'M GONNA TRY AND ACCESS
THE GOVERNMENT'S DATABASE

02:20.106 --> 02:23.142
AND BREAK IN TO THEIR SYSTEM
TO FIND OUT WHO FRAMED WATSON.

02:23.209 --> 02:25.578
SOMEONE WITH POWER IS
PROTECTING A CHILD KILLER.

02:25.645 --> 02:27.280
I NEED TO FIND OUT WHO !

02:27.347 --> 02:30.350
AND NOW "SPAWN",
SO TURN OFF YOUR LIGHTS.

03:28.474 --> 03:32.679
WARRIORS CAN FEEL FORCES
MASSING AGAINST THEM.

03:32.745 --> 03:35.515
THE AGONIZING WAIT
FOR BATTLE

03:35.582 --> 03:37.850
BECOMES A WAY OF LIFE.

03:37.917 --> 03:41.154
TURNING AND TWISTING
THEIR DARK SOULS.

03:41.220 --> 03:43.456
FEEDING TENSE RAGE

03:43.523 --> 03:47.060
THAT BOILS DEEP
IN EVERY HELL SPAWN.

03:47.126 --> 03:50.263
A RAGE OF THE UNFAIRNESS
OF THEIR PLIGHT

03:50.330 --> 03:53.232
AND A FEELING
STILL DEEPER,

03:53.299 --> 03:56.669
THAT THEY'VE
EARNED IT.

03:56.736 --> 03:58.371
( dispatcher )
ALL UNITS RESPOND
TO KIDNAP,

03:58.438 --> 04:00.239
MADISON AND
43rd STREET.

04:00.306 --> 04:01.708
( male )
WHO IS THIS FREAK ?

04:01.774 --> 04:02.875
WITNESSES FIGURE HIM
FOR SOME KIND OF

04:02.942 --> 04:04.544
WHACKED OUT
STREET PREACHER.

04:04.611 --> 04:07.080
COULD BE THAT CHILD KILLER
HOMICIDE'S BEEN HUNTING.

04:08.381 --> 04:10.183
WELL, WHOEVER THE
BASTARD IS HE'S DEAD.

04:10.249 --> 04:11.985
HE JUST DOESN'T
KNOW IT YET.

04:12.051 --> 04:14.253
( radio )
Suspect holding
possible kidnap victim...

04:14.320 --> 04:16.189
GOT THAT RIGHT.

04:18.157 --> 04:19.859
DID I SAY I WAS
GONNA KILL ANYBODY ?

04:19.926 --> 04:21.794
NO, I NEVER SAID THAT.

04:21.861 --> 04:23.930
NOW I MAY HAVE
DONE THAT...

04:23.997 --> 04:26.966
BUT I NEVER SAID I WAS
GONNA KILL ANYBODY.

04:27.033 --> 04:30.136
SEE, SAYING
AND DOING

04:30.203 --> 04:33.172
ARE TWO VERY
DIFFERENT THINGS.

04:33.239 --> 04:34.741
DON'T YOU THINK ?

04:34.807 --> 04:38.277
NOW, YOU WOULDN'T
JUST BE SAYING THAT

04:38.344 --> 04:41.314
'CAUSE I GOT THIS
GRENADE IN MY HANDS.

04:41.381 --> 04:43.316
( bystander )
THIS GUY'S NUTS.

04:45.451 --> 04:46.886
KILLING KIDS,

04:46.953 --> 04:49.555
THAT'S ABOUT CATCHING
THE INNOCENCE, YOU KNOW ?

04:49.622 --> 04:52.792
LIFE, DEATH, GOOD, EVIL,
IT'S ALL RIGHT HERE !

04:52.859 --> 04:55.662
WINDOWS TO
THE SOUL, BOYS.

04:55.728 --> 04:58.197
TAKE A PEEK,
SEE THE PARTY ?

04:58.264 --> 04:59.966
( sirens )

05:01.100 --> 05:04.937
YOU SHOULD HAVE
TOLD THEM, NO SIRENS !

05:05.004 --> 05:07.206
( Gareb )
OH SHIT !

05:13.880 --> 05:16.082
HOLY SHIT !

05:19.619 --> 05:21.721
( street preacher )
WHAT... NO APPLAUSE ?!

05:21.788 --> 05:23.256
NO APPRECIATION !

05:23.322 --> 05:26.059
WHAT IS THIS WORLD
COMING TO ?!

05:32.265 --> 05:33.966
( mumbling )

05:34.033 --> 05:36.369
YOU KNOW
SOMETHING ?

05:36.436 --> 05:39.305
I HATE THAT !

05:39.372 --> 05:40.840
IF YOU LIKE
THOSE HANDS,

05:40.907 --> 05:42.375
I SUGGEST YOU PUT
THEM IN YOUR POCKET

05:42.442 --> 05:43.609
OR YOUR PANTS
OR WHEREVER !

05:43.676 --> 05:45.778
JUST GET THEM
OUT OF MY FACE !

05:47.447 --> 05:49.048
AHH !

05:58.224 --> 06:00.193
( preacher )
ADAM !

06:00.259 --> 06:04.397
I KNOW YOU CAN'T HEAR ME
BUT I DON'T GIVE A SHIT !

06:04.464 --> 06:07.500
GET YOUR PUNY LITTLE ASS
OUT HERE, NOW !!

06:16.909 --> 06:19.479
OH, SOMEBODY ELSE
WANNA PLAY ?

06:19.545 --> 06:22.515
HOW'S ABOUT A QUICK
GAME OF CATCH ?

06:22.582 --> 06:25.418
C'MON, WHAT
DO YOU SAY ?

06:26.919 --> 06:29.088
LET'S GO, KID.

06:29.155 --> 06:32.458
GUESS THE RATS WOULD RATHER
PLAY WITH THEMSELVES.

06:35.595 --> 06:37.497
( laughing )

06:45.505 --> 06:46.873
( radio )
... officers down,

06:46.939 --> 06:48.608
suspect went southbound
through alley,

06:48.674 --> 06:50.710
requesting help.

07:00.620 --> 07:02.688
SHIT, THERE MAN,
WE GOT HIM !

07:05.491 --> 07:08.394
RADIO FOR BACKUP THEN
SWING AROUND THE SOUTH END.

07:08.461 --> 07:10.263
SUSPECT SIGHTED,
OFFICER IN PURSUIT.

07:10.329 --> 07:11.731
REQUEST IMMEDIATE BACKUP.

07:13.032 --> 07:14.467
( radio )
All units stand-by.

07:14.534 --> 07:16.402
Officers requesting backup
for kidnap suspect.

07:16.469 --> 07:18.337
WE GOT THIS
ASSHOLE !

07:18.404 --> 07:21.474
WE'RE 20, MADISON
AND 43rd STREET.

07:22.341 --> 07:24.177
BOTTOM'S UP...

07:24.243 --> 07:26.412
BIG GUY !

07:26.479 --> 07:28.014
AHHH !

07:31.551 --> 07:33.419
JESUS, GOD !

07:33.486 --> 07:36.589
OFFICER DOWN,
REPEAT OFFICER DOWN !

07:36.656 --> 07:38.024
GOD !

07:39.158 --> 07:41.460
( radio )
Requesting help,
officer down, officer down.

07:41.527 --> 07:42.995
Madison and
43rd street.

07:45.131 --> 07:47.400
6-Adam-15 come in,
6-Adam-15 come in !

07:47.466 --> 07:48.668
What's your
location ?

08:01.280 --> 08:03.015
OH, AL.

08:03.082 --> 08:05.017
I LOVE YOU, WANDA.

08:05.084 --> 08:07.220
MAYBE IT'S TIME
WE START THINKING ABOUT

08:07.286 --> 08:09.188
HAVING A REAL
FAMILY.

08:10.890 --> 08:12.091
AHH !

08:18.297 --> 08:19.265
MOMMY !

08:20.733 --> 08:22.268
CYAN !

08:27.173 --> 08:28.975
( gunshots )

08:30.476 --> 08:32.578
HOLY CHRIST !

08:32.645 --> 08:34.947
C'MON YOU WORTHLESS,
COCKSUCKER !

08:35.014 --> 08:37.817
TRY TO BLOW ME UP,
YOU SON-OF-A-BITCH !

08:40.253 --> 08:42.221
I'LL KILL YOU...
COME ON !!

08:42.288 --> 08:44.056
WHERE IS HE ?

08:44.123 --> 08:46.492
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT, WHERE'S WHO ?

08:46.559 --> 08:49.595
LISTEN ASSHOLE,
I'M NOT IN THE FUCKING MOOD !

08:49.662 --> 08:53.165
YOUR PREACHER FRIEND,
HE WAS DRAGGING A BOY.

08:53.232 --> 08:56.369
I CAN'T HELP YOU,
I DIDN'T SEE ANY...

08:58.638 --> 09:01.207
I SWEAR TO GOD,
I DON'T KNOW NOTHING !

09:01.274 --> 09:02.909
PLEASE.

09:02.975 --> 09:05.278
I TOLD YOU I WANT
SOME GODAMN ANSWERS

09:05.344 --> 09:07.246
AND I WANT THEM
RIGHT NOW !

09:08.547 --> 09:11.584
( Spawn )
IS THIS HOW YOU
PROTECT AND SERVE ?

09:11.651 --> 09:13.286
SHIT !

09:19.659 --> 09:22.161
I CLOCKED HIM,
I KNOW IT.

09:33.606 --> 09:35.241
BACK OFF,
SHIT-FACE !

09:35.308 --> 09:37.276
I'LL DO YOUR PAL.

09:56.929 --> 09:59.031
WHO MADE YOU GOD,
LITTLE MAN ?

09:59.098 --> 10:01.734
NOT THAT GUN,
NOT THAT UNIFORM.

10:01.801 --> 10:02.969
NOTHING.

10:07.873 --> 10:09.608
YOU WANT TO
SCARE PEOPLE, FINE.

10:09.675 --> 10:12.011
I NEED A SCARECROW.

10:12.078 --> 10:14.480
YOU'RE GONNA BE MY
PERSONAL MESSAGE BOARD.

10:14.547 --> 10:16.315
I WANT EVERYONE
TO SEE WHAT HAPPENS

10:16.382 --> 10:19.185
WHEN THEY COME
HERE UNINVITED.

10:23.322 --> 10:27.159
( preacher )
NOW ISN'T THIS A DELICIOUS
LITTLE SITUATION ?

10:28.961 --> 10:31.597
YOU KNOW,
PEOPLE REALLY

10:31.664 --> 10:33.866
SHOULD FINISH
WHAT THEY START.

10:35.534 --> 10:37.136
AHH !

10:38.804 --> 10:40.706
BUT I SAY TO YOU,

10:40.773 --> 10:43.876
FAIR IS FAIR
AND THAT'S AMERICAN.

10:43.943 --> 10:46.412
THE REASON THIS BILL
IS SO CONTROVERSIAL,

10:46.479 --> 10:49.015
IS BECAUSE IT'S NOT CONCERNED
WITH THE BOTTOM LINE.

10:49.081 --> 10:51.083
IT'S CONCERNED
WITH THE FAMILY,

10:51.150 --> 10:53.652
WHICH IS THE BACKBONE
OF THIS COUNTRY.

10:53.719 --> 10:57.123
WE MUST TAKE A STAND
AND IF SUCCESSFUL,

10:57.189 --> 11:00.459
IT WILL ENABLE US TO
THRIVE AS THE GREATEST COUNTRY

11:00.526 --> 11:01.961
IN THE WORLD.

11:02.028 --> 11:04.063
THANK YOU.

11:04.130 --> 11:06.132
SENATOR, SENATOR,
SENATOR...

11:06.198 --> 11:07.833
( reporter )
ARE YOU SAYING
THAT YOU WILL VOTE FOR

11:07.900 --> 11:09.402
THE FAMILY RELIEF
BILL TODAY,

11:09.468 --> 11:11.670
IN SPITE OF SOME OF THE
RESISTANCE FROM CAPITAL HILL ?

11:11.737 --> 11:12.905
YOU HEARD
MY SPEECH.

11:12.972 --> 11:14.907
I'M NOT HERE TO
FIGHT THE SENATE, MA'AM.

11:14.974 --> 11:16.208
I'M HERE TO
HELP AMERICA.

11:16.275 --> 11:17.009
THAT'S WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT.

11:17.076 --> 11:18.310
SENATOR, ONE
MORE QUESTION...

11:18.377 --> 11:19.779
THANKS EVERYONE.

11:26.318 --> 11:28.521
NOW, LET'S GET
SOME REAL FOOD.

11:29.955 --> 11:32.258
( phone rings )

11:32.324 --> 11:33.426
YEAH.

11:33.492 --> 11:36.662
( Wynn )
Ignoring my calls
is not a smart idea.

11:38.197 --> 11:39.265
RUNNING FOR
PRESIDENT

11:39.331 --> 11:41.233
IS NOT LIKE WORKING
FOR THE POST OFFICE,

11:41.300 --> 11:42.501
I HAVE OBLIGATIONS.

11:42.568 --> 11:45.104
LISTEN TO ME
VERY CAREFULLY, SENATOR.

11:45.171 --> 11:47.473
YOUR EVERY STEP,
EVERY THOUGHT, EVERY<i> BREATH,</i>

11:47.540 --> 11:49.942
IS TO BE CLEARED THROUGH ME,
IS THAT UNDERSTOOD ?

11:50.009 --> 11:52.244
YOU COMPROMISED
BOTH OUR POSITIONS.

11:52.311 --> 11:53.379
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT ?

11:53.446 --> 11:56.449
THAT BILL HAS SEVERAL
AMENDMENTS TACKED TO IT

11:56.515 --> 11:57.983
THAT WORK AGAINST
MY INTERESTS.

11:58.050 --> 11:59.251
I'll get them
severed,

11:59.318 --> 12:02.221
THAT WAY I CAN
PRESERVE MY STANCE.

12:02.288 --> 12:04.590
NO, UNLIKE ME, YOU DON'T
HAVE THAT KIND OF POWER.

12:04.657 --> 12:06.492
These cutbacks
are locked in

12:06.559 --> 12:08.127
so the entire bill
must fail.

12:08.194 --> 12:09.528
NOW, I'M GOING TO HAVE TO
PULL IN SOME FAVORS

12:09.595 --> 12:11.097
TO NEGATE YOUR VOTE

12:11.163 --> 12:12.731
and save you from
looking like a fool.

12:12.798 --> 12:14.600
SCREW UP AGAIN,
SCOTTY,

12:14.667 --> 12:17.436
AND YOUR POLITICAL
CAREER IS OVER.

12:20.473 --> 12:21.740
EXCUSE ME SENATOR,

12:21.807 --> 12:22.908
WHERE WILL YOU
BE DINING ?

12:22.975 --> 12:24.410
SHUT UP AND DRIVE.

12:27.446 --> 12:29.515
( radio )
Kidnap suspect last seen
Madison and 43rd.

12:29.582 --> 12:31.183
( Burke )
JESUS, WHAT A MESS !

12:31.250 --> 12:33.385
WHEN DID A THREAT FROM
A GRENADE-TOTING PSYCHO

12:33.452 --> 12:36.055
GET TREATED LIKE A TYPICAL
FREAKING PURSE SNATCHING ?!

12:36.122 --> 12:38.057
WHO DROPPED
THE BALL ON THIS ?!

12:38.124 --> 12:40.926
MAKES IT LOOK LIKE
A BUNCH OF COPS FROM L.A. !

12:40.993 --> 12:42.361
WHAT YOU GOT
OVER THERE, TWITCH ?

12:42.428 --> 12:46.732
GRENADE FRAGMENTS
AND A BIG HOLE, SIR.

12:46.799 --> 12:49.301
GIVE ME SOMETHING
I CAN WORK WITH.

12:49.368 --> 12:51.337
WELL SIR, THIS IS
THE SAME ALLEY WHERE

12:51.403 --> 12:53.572
WE FOUND THE BODY OF
THAT REPORTER STEVENS.

12:53.639 --> 12:55.341
I KNOW AND THEM
DEAD KIDS WERE DROPPED

12:55.407 --> 12:56.442
IN THIS AREA TOO.

12:56.509 --> 12:58.444
SEEMS TO BE
A POPULAR SPOT.

12:58.511 --> 13:00.513
BUT IS IT A
COINCIDENCE ?

13:00.579 --> 13:02.648
STEVENS TAPED
CONVERSATIONS

13:02.715 --> 13:04.450
SEEMED TO SUGGEST
A CONNECTION

13:04.517 --> 13:06.585
BETWEEN WASHINGTON
AND A CHILD KILLER.

13:06.652 --> 13:08.287
I SWEAR THEY'RE MAKING
THESE THINGS SMALLER.

13:08.354 --> 13:11.490
SIR, I REALLY NEED TO
GET BACK TO THOSE TAPES.

13:11.557 --> 13:13.125
LATER, TWITCH.

13:13.192 --> 13:16.195
THIS SO CALLED "PREACHER"
JUST MIGHT BE OUR CHILD KILLER.

13:16.262 --> 13:18.197
AND I WANT HIS ASS
BEFORE THE FEDS SMELL A HEADLINE

13:18.264 --> 13:20.099
AND TAKE US OUT
OF THE LOOP !

13:20.166 --> 13:22.234
( clanking )

13:25.004 --> 13:25.804
OH, JESUS !

13:27.740 --> 13:29.441
OH MY GOD !

13:29.508 --> 13:31.377
GET HIM OUT
OF THERE !

13:36.115 --> 13:38.450
... STAY OUT...

13:38.517 --> 13:40.386
... HIS ALLEYS...

13:40.452 --> 13:41.820
... TWO OF 'EM.

13:41.887 --> 13:43.789
WHAT ABOUT
THE PREACHER ?

13:44.857 --> 13:47.526
... RED CLOAK...

13:47.593 --> 13:49.128
RED WHAT ?

13:49.195 --> 13:50.930
I THINK HE
SAID "CLOAK", SIR.

13:50.996 --> 13:52.731
WHAT'S THAT GOTTA DO WITH
THE DAMN PREACHER ?

13:52.798 --> 13:55.367
( gurgling )

13:56.802 --> 13:59.371
CHRIST, MEDICS,
GET OVER HERE !

14:01.073 --> 14:02.541
TWITCH, RADIO
HEADQUARTERS.

14:02.608 --> 14:04.843
TELL THEM S.W.A.T.'s GONNA
LOCK DOWN A SIX BLOCK RADIUS.

14:04.910 --> 14:06.512
WE'RE GONNA
"PINCH" THIS AREA

14:06.579 --> 14:08.347
'TIL I FIND THAT
FUCKING LUNATIC !

14:11.417 --> 14:14.220
RETRIEVING THOSE WEAPONS
HAS BECOME CRITICAL.

14:14.286 --> 14:17.856
THE SLIGHTEST DELAY CAN
SHIFT POLITICAL BALANCES.

14:17.923 --> 14:20.359
( beeping )
Terry to see you, sir.

14:21.627 --> 14:23.596
TERRY, COME IN.

14:23.662 --> 14:27.199
SIR, MY INVESTIGATION
OF THE WEAPON SHIPMENT

14:27.266 --> 14:29.201
HASN'T TURNED UP
ANYTHING.

14:29.268 --> 14:31.170
THE ONLY GOOD NEWS IS
NO OTHER SHIPMENTS

14:31.237 --> 14:32.504
ARE CURRENTLY
MISSING.

14:32.571 --> 14:34.740
AND WHAT ARE WE DOING TO LOCATE
THE WEAPONS WE'VE LOST ?

14:34.807 --> 14:36.575
WELL SIR,
WITHOUT A LEAD,

14:36.642 --> 14:39.278
WE'RE STILL SHOOTING
IN THE DARK, SO TO SPEAK.

14:39.345 --> 14:41.046
I SUSPECT A CHINESE
TERRORIST GROUP

14:41.113 --> 14:42.514
OR THE
CALI CARTEL.

14:42.581 --> 14:44.483
BOTH ARE LINKED TO
RECENT ESPIONAGE ATTACKS

14:44.550 --> 14:45.818
IN EUROPEAN ARMORIES.

14:45.884 --> 14:47.620
I'LL HAVE FULL STATISTICAL
READ-OUTS IN THE MORNING.

14:47.686 --> 14:48.754
GOOD WORK.

14:48.821 --> 14:50.356
LEAVE THIS FILE
ON MY DESK.

14:50.422 --> 14:52.524
WE'LL DISCUSS THIS FURTHER
AFTER I READ IT.

15:04.370 --> 15:06.705
I DON'T LIKE HIDING
IN GODAMN CLOSETS !

15:06.772 --> 15:10.175
WELL, YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED
TO BE IN THE COUNTRY, CHAPEL.

15:10.242 --> 15:13.279
ISN'T THAT THE GUY WHO
MARRIED AL SIMMONS' WIFE ?

15:13.345 --> 15:14.880
AS I WAS SAYING,

15:14.947 --> 15:16.715
WE HAVE TO CAREFULLY
POSITION OURSELVES SO...

15:16.782 --> 15:18.250
YOU KNOW,
HE SHOULD THANK ME

15:18.317 --> 15:20.886
FOR FREEING UP A NICE
PIECE OF ASS LIKE WANDA.

15:20.953 --> 15:22.655
LET'S FOCUS.

15:22.721 --> 15:25.024
THE GUNS, THAT'S
WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

15:25.090 --> 15:26.325
NOTHING ELSE.

15:26.392 --> 15:27.860
NOT WORRIED ABOUT
THE BOY SCOUT ?

15:27.926 --> 15:29.395
TERRY IS BEING
MONITORED.

15:29.461 --> 15:31.196
JUST LIKE
EVERYONE ELSE.

15:31.263 --> 15:33.065
SOMEONE'S GOT
YOUR WEAPONS.

15:33.132 --> 15:34.566
THERE'S A LEAK
SOMEWHERE.

15:34.633 --> 15:36.035
I NEED IT PLUGGED.

15:36.101 --> 15:38.537
JUST LET ME KNOW
WHEN AND WHERE.

15:38.604 --> 15:40.039
I WANT THIS
MISSION EXECUTED

15:40.105 --> 15:41.807
WITH PRECISION
AND FINESSE.

15:41.874 --> 15:43.275
YOU'RE TRYING
TO SAY I'M SLOPPY ?

15:43.342 --> 15:46.612
OVERZEALOUS LIKE OUR LITTLE
SOUTH AMERICAN PROJECT.

15:46.679 --> 15:49.315
NOT MY FAULT THOSE PEOPLE
DON'T KNOW HOW TO DUCK.

15:49.381 --> 15:52.017
THIS TIME IT'S
ON AMERICAN SOIL.

15:52.084 --> 15:54.153
THE RULES ARE DIFFERENT
COVER YOUR TRACKS.

15:54.219 --> 15:56.789
YEAH, YEAH, JUST
CALL THE BALL.

15:56.855 --> 15:59.358
SO I CAN GET OUT OF
YOUR FUCKING CLOSET.

15:59.425 --> 16:00.492
( phone )

16:00.559 --> 16:01.927
NOW WHAT ?

16:03.562 --> 16:05.431
WYNN, WE'VE
GOT A PROBLEM.

16:05.497 --> 16:06.565
I'm listening.

16:06.632 --> 16:08.334
INTERNAL DATA
MONITORING IN D.C.

16:08.400 --> 16:10.302
SUGGESTS SOMEONE'S BEEN
HACKING INTO THE FILES

16:10.369 --> 16:11.837
OF SEVERAL
POLITICIANS.

16:11.904 --> 16:13.305
INCLUDING ME.

16:13.372 --> 16:16.375
Don't worry, I sanitized
your political record.

16:16.442 --> 16:18.777
PERSONAL INFORMATION,
FAMILY HISTORY.

16:18.844 --> 16:21.680
I'm scared shitless,
I can't take my mind off it.

16:21.747 --> 16:24.917
THE KYLE WATSON SITUATION
GOT OUT OF CONTROL.

16:24.983 --> 16:27.619
That lawyer,
Wanda Blake,

16:27.686 --> 16:28.687
IT MUST BE HER.

16:28.754 --> 16:31.357
ONE OF MY GUYS GOT
KNOCKED OFF TRAILING HER.

16:31.423 --> 16:34.093
I HAD ASSUMED SHE'D
DROP HER INVESTIGATION

16:34.159 --> 16:36.228
ONCE HER PLAN GOT OFF.

16:36.295 --> 16:40.132
SHE'S GOT SOME EX-COP DIGGING
INTO DEEP EVIDENCE FILES.

16:40.199 --> 16:42.234
HE'S GOT ENOUGH
CONNECTIONS IN THE DEPARTMENT

16:42.301 --> 16:44.837
to turn up some
very ugly shit.

16:44.903 --> 16:47.606
SO WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO DO ?

16:47.673 --> 16:50.309
Stay calm,
run for President.

16:50.376 --> 16:51.944
I'LL TAKE CARE
OF THE REST.

16:53.545 --> 16:57.282
IS EVERYONE USELESS
AROUND HERE ?!

16:57.349 --> 16:59.685
TROUBLE IN
PARADISE ?

16:59.752 --> 17:02.187
WANDA BLAKE,
STIRRING UP TROUBLE.

17:02.254 --> 17:04.723
MAYBE TERRY'S
RUBBING OFF ON HER.

17:04.790 --> 17:05.758
TIME IS SHORT.

17:05.824 --> 17:07.226
FIRST, LET'S GET
YOU ON TARGET.

17:07.292 --> 17:10.195
( phone )

17:10.262 --> 17:11.397
( Tony )
YEAH ?

17:11.463 --> 17:13.966
I want you to find that
thing in the alley.

17:14.032 --> 17:16.101
I have a specialist
who will deal with it.

17:16.168 --> 17:18.670
Second, I need a
pick up and delivery.

17:18.737 --> 17:20.873
A child,
nothing serious.

17:20.939 --> 17:22.574
Someone will contact
you with the details.

17:22.641 --> 17:23.809
GOT IT.

17:25.377 --> 17:27.479
KIM, CALL SENATOR McMILLAN
AND TELL HIM

17:27.546 --> 17:30.482
THE PROBLEM WE DISCUSSED
IS BEING RESOLVED.

17:30.549 --> 17:33.819
TWIST WILL FIND THIS FREAK,
THEN YOU'RE ON.

17:33.886 --> 17:37.156
GET THE GUNS FIRST,
THEN ASK YOUR QUESTIONS.

17:37.222 --> 17:39.124
AND REMEMBER,
FINESSE.

17:39.191 --> 17:40.359
GOT IT.

17:40.426 --> 17:42.594
LIKE KIDNAPING YOUR
EMPLOYEE'S BABY.

17:42.661 --> 17:43.896
A DETAIL.

17:43.962 --> 17:45.798
I ALWAYS DID LIKE
WORKING FOR YOU.

17:56.575 --> 17:58.243
( male )
OH MY GOD !

17:58.310 --> 17:59.344
HOLY SHIT !

17:59.411 --> 18:03.282
( Bobby )
JESUS AL, WHAT'D
YOU DO TO HIM ?

18:03.348 --> 18:06.084
WHAT HAPPENED HERE,
WHO MOVED HIM ?!

18:06.151 --> 18:08.353
I WANT ANSWERS !

18:08.420 --> 18:11.023
( Gareb )
COME ON AL, NONE OF US
WOULD TOUCH HIM.

18:11.089 --> 18:12.424
WE KNOW YOU'D...

18:12.491 --> 18:13.959
YOU KNOW NOTHING
ABOUT ME !

18:14.026 --> 18:15.594
NONE OF YOU DO !

18:15.661 --> 18:18.897
OUT OF MY WAY.

18:22.534 --> 18:25.337
( Cogliostro )
GIVE THEM A CHANCE OR
LEAVE THEM THE HELL ALONE !

18:25.404 --> 18:27.172
GET OUT OF
MY WAY, OLD MAN.

18:27.239 --> 18:28.574
YOU'RE SAVING
THEM ONE MINUTE,

18:28.640 --> 18:30.742
THEN SPITTING ON
THEM THE NEXT !

18:30.809 --> 18:32.978
MAKE UP YOUR MIND, SPAWN.

18:33.045 --> 18:35.013
ARE YOU GONNA
DO WHAT'S RIGHT

18:35.080 --> 18:37.449
OR SIT HERE ON
YOUR ASS AND BROOD ?!

18:37.516 --> 18:39.852
THAT LITTLE BOY,
EARLIER TODAY,

18:39.918 --> 18:42.454
HE'S STILL WITH
THAT PSYCHOPATH.

18:42.521 --> 18:46.391
YOU COULD HAVE DONE
SOMETHING BUT YOU DIDN'T.

18:46.458 --> 18:48.026
WHY ?

18:48.093 --> 18:49.795
HE DIDN'T
ASK FOR HELP.

18:49.862 --> 18:50.996
HE'S MUTE.

18:51.063 --> 18:53.098
HIS PROBLEM,
NOT MINE.

18:53.165 --> 18:55.834
LOOK, YOU CAN'T PUSH
PEOPLE OUT OF THE WAY,

18:55.901 --> 18:57.903
LOOKING FOR YOUR
PERSONAL SPACE

18:57.970 --> 19:00.539
AND EXPECT THEM
NOT TO PUSH BACK.

19:00.606 --> 19:02.808
YOU KILL HIT-MEN,
THE MOB COME.

19:02.875 --> 19:05.544
YOU STICK A COP ON
THE WALL, THE POLICE COME.

19:05.611 --> 19:09.581
THESE BUMS, THEY'RE
JUST INNOCENT BYSTANDERS,

19:09.648 --> 19:11.984
CAUGHT IN THE MIDDLE
OF YOUR STORM.

19:12.050 --> 19:13.218
WHATEVER.

19:13.285 --> 19:14.920
YOU HAVE A
PURPOSE SPAWN.

19:14.987 --> 19:17.890
WHETHER YOU WANT
TO BELIEVE IT OR NOT.

19:17.956 --> 19:21.493
THE SOONER YOU ACCEPT IT,
THE BETTER OFF YOU'LL BE.

19:23.962 --> 19:26.331
( humming )

19:26.398 --> 19:29.568
♪ I LOVE ICE CREAM ♪

19:32.971 --> 19:34.573
HELLO, BILLY.

19:34.640 --> 19:36.642
HOW DO YOU
KNOW MY NAME ?

19:36.708 --> 19:38.810
I'M A FAN.

19:38.877 --> 19:40.145
A WHAT ?

19:40.212 --> 19:41.713
A FAN.

19:41.780 --> 19:43.615
BEEN ADMIRING
YOUR WORK

19:43.682 --> 19:45.350
FOR QUITE SOME
TIME NOW ACTUALLY.

19:45.417 --> 19:46.518
WHY ?

19:46.585 --> 19:48.186
I JUST LOVE TO SEE
THE CHILDREN'S FACES

19:48.253 --> 19:49.521
WHEN YOU'RE
WITH THEM.

19:49.588 --> 19:51.490
YOU LIKE KIDS,
DON'T YOU BILLY ?

19:51.557 --> 19:53.458
YEAH.

19:53.525 --> 19:55.427
ME TOO.

19:57.029 --> 19:59.765
BUT I'M A CLOWN,
I'M SUPPOSED TO.

20:01.099 --> 20:03.569
HEY YOU WANNA
GO TO A PARTY ?

20:03.635 --> 20:04.636
WHEN ?

20:04.703 --> 20:06.505
LATER TONIGHT,
ACROSS TOWN.

20:06.572 --> 20:08.840
IT WILL BE
A REAL SCREAM.

20:08.907 --> 20:11.009
I PROMISE.

20:23.121 --> 20:24.590
( reporter )
The investigation
has now officially

20:24.656 --> 20:27.459
turned into a
full-scale manhunt.

20:27.526 --> 20:29.161
Very few details
have been released.

20:29.227 --> 20:31.396
We have confirmation that
at least one officer

20:31.463 --> 20:33.498
has been killed
at this point.

20:33.565 --> 20:34.866
Also just in,

20:34.933 --> 20:36.535
the senate has
narrowly defeated

20:36.602 --> 20:38.437
the Federal Relief
Taxation Bill,

20:38.503 --> 20:40.339
spearheaded
by Senator McMillan,

20:40.405 --> 20:41.940
who received much
opposition

20:42.007 --> 20:44.476
from both Republicans
and Democrats.

20:44.543 --> 20:46.211
McMillan,
who plans to run

20:46.278 --> 20:47.813
in the next
presidential election

20:47.879 --> 20:49.915
has been unavailable
for comment.

20:49.982 --> 20:51.416
READY CYAN ?

20:52.818 --> 20:54.586
GREAT CATCH, HONEY.

20:56.622 --> 20:58.090
GOOD JOB.

20:58.156 --> 20:59.658
( phone )

20:59.725 --> 21:02.628
C'MON HONEY, MOMMY HAS TO
GO INSIDE FOR A MOMENT.

21:10.068 --> 21:11.336
HELLO.

21:11.403 --> 21:13.338
YES, THIS IS SHE.

21:13.405 --> 21:16.842
YES, I KNOW
MAX KIVALA.

21:16.908 --> 21:20.612
OH GOD, NO,
NOT MAX !

21:20.679 --> 21:22.681
NO !

21:22.748 --> 21:25.884
WHEN... HOW ?

21:25.951 --> 21:28.220
YES, HE WORKED
FOR ME.

21:28.286 --> 21:30.122
WHEN DID
THIS HAPPEN ?

21:32.357 --> 21:34.826
NO, YOU DO NOT HAVE
A RIGHT TO KNOW

21:34.893 --> 21:36.662
WHAT WE WERE
WORKING ON.

21:36.728 --> 21:38.730
HIS WIFE,
YES, I KNOW HER.

21:38.797 --> 21:40.999
I WANT TO HEAR
THAT FROM HER.

21:41.066 --> 21:43.402
I DON'T TRUST... CYAN ?

21:43.468 --> 21:44.936
CYAN ?

21:45.003 --> 21:47.472
CYAN ?

21:49.107 --> 21:50.709
CYAN...

21:50.776 --> 21:53.545
CYAN, WHERE
ARE YOU HONEY ?

21:54.646 --> 21:55.847
CYAN...

21:58.684 --> 22:01.353
CYAN !

22:03.889 --> 22:06.358
( radio warble )

22:07.793 --> 22:09.861
HELL'S SPAWNS
BEGIN TO TAKE SIDES

22:09.928 --> 22:11.730
IN THEIR OWN MINDS.

22:11.797 --> 22:14.599
RIGHT, WRONG,
MORAL, IMMORAL,

22:14.666 --> 22:17.803
GOOD, EVIL.

22:17.869 --> 22:21.840
NONE ARE EVER SURE
WHERE THEY WILL FALL.

22:21.907 --> 22:24.109
WHATCHA DOING
WITH THE HEATERS ?

22:24.176 --> 22:26.778
LOTS OF UNFRIENDLY TRAFFIC
FLOWING THROUGH HERE.

22:29.314 --> 22:30.782
SO THAT'S IT NOW ?

22:30.849 --> 22:32.784
IT'S BECOME
AN EYE FOR AN EYE ?

22:32.851 --> 22:34.386
LISTEN OLD MAN,

22:34.453 --> 22:36.455
THE GOVERNMENT
TAUGHT ME HOW TO FIGHT,

22:36.521 --> 22:37.789
HOW TO KILL.

22:37.856 --> 22:39.458
IT'S ALL
I'VE GOT LEFT.

22:39.524 --> 22:40.959
IF YOU DON'T HAVE
THE STOMACH FOR IT,

22:41.026 --> 22:42.427
GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE.

22:42.494 --> 22:44.029
( radio )
All units,

22:44.096 --> 22:46.431
report of a child kidnaping
on the south side of Queens.

22:46.498 --> 22:48.967
Female, approximately
four-years-old.

22:49.034 --> 22:50.969
Answers to
the name of Cyan.

22:51.036 --> 22:52.404
Units are rolling...

22:52.471 --> 22:53.905
CYAN !

22:53.972 --> 22:55.207
YOU KNOW HER ?

22:55.273 --> 22:57.976
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO ?

22:59.144 --> 23:01.613
YOU GONNA HELP
GET THE KID BACK ?

23:05.851 --> 23:08.754
( Burke )
ATTENTION ASSHOLES,
THIS IS THE POLICE.

23:08.820 --> 23:10.756
DROP ALL WEAPONS.

23:10.822 --> 23:13.558
COME OUT WITH YOUR HANDS
OVER YOUR HEADS.

23:13.625 --> 23:15.293
TWITCH, I OUGHT TO
YANK YOUR DICK OFF !

23:15.360 --> 23:16.628
WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN ?

23:16.695 --> 23:18.764
WE GOT THIS COP-KILLING
KIDNAPING BASTARD CORNERED,

23:18.830 --> 23:20.899
AND HE AIN'T
GETTING AWAY.

23:32.477 --> 23:34.346
( Burke )
HOLD YOUR FIRE.

23:34.412 --> 23:36.148
OKAY PREACHER,
JUST LET THE BOY GO

23:36.214 --> 23:37.516
AND NO ONE HAS TO
GET HURT HERE.

23:37.582 --> 23:40.152
OH, YES SOMEONE DOES.

23:40.218 --> 23:41.987
HE'S ARMED.

23:42.053 --> 23:45.590
DON'T BE A FOOL,
CALM DOWN.

23:45.657 --> 23:48.760
YOU DON'T WANT TO DO
ANYTHING STUPID.

23:48.827 --> 23:50.228
JUST GIVE ME
THE GRENADE

23:50.295 --> 23:51.530
AND I PROMISE YOU,

23:51.596 --> 23:53.265
YOU AND THE BOY
WILL BE PROTECTED.

23:53.331 --> 23:54.733
SURE.

24:02.574 --> 24:04.943
IT'S OKAY,
STILL GOT A PIN.

24:06.511 --> 24:08.647
EVERYTHING'S FINE...

24:08.713 --> 24:11.817
WELL,
NOT QUITE.

24:11.883 --> 24:13.351
NOBODY MOVE !

24:31.203 --> 24:32.370
( radio )
Do you have him ?

24:32.437 --> 24:34.506
UH-HUH.

24:36.274 --> 24:37.442
Drop him.

24:37.509 --> 24:39.144
( gunshot )

24:49.421 --> 24:51.256
( male )
GODAMMIT !

24:59.664 --> 25:01.533
NICE SHOT.

25:02.601 --> 25:04.169
( Burke )
HOLY SHIT !

25:06.037 --> 25:08.473
HOLY SHIT, GO DOWN,
EVERYBODY DOWN !

25:25.824 --> 25:28.093
FINALLY, HAVING
CHOSEN A SIDE

25:28.159 --> 25:30.929
AND RELEASED
OF SOME INNER GUILT,

25:30.996 --> 25:33.832
THE WARRIOR
IS NOW FREE TO PURSUE

25:33.899 --> 25:36.735
HIS PERSONAL
MISSION, UNFETTERED.

25:36.801 --> 25:39.871
GOD HELP THOSE
IN HIS PATH.

25:56.922 --> 25:58.757
( clown )
GLAD TO BE OUT
OF THAT SKIN.

25:58.823 --> 26:00.592
THAT WAS TIGHT.

26:00.659 --> 26:02.494
ESPECIALLY IN
THE CROTCH.

26:10.602 --> 26:13.238
( Cyan crying )

26:16.942 --> 26:19.177
( knocking )

26:19.244 --> 26:23.481
MOVE FROM THIS SPOT AND
YOU'LL BE SORRY, GIRLIE.

26:26.518 --> 26:28.253
AHH !

26:35.193 --> 26:36.962
HELLO LITTLE GIRL.

26:37.028 --> 26:39.731
DO YOU LIKE
TOOTIE-FRUITIE ?

